; Regression test for issue #1593: ledger and currency format in entry command (BZ#521)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1593
;
; When using the xact/entry command with a non-default currency (e.g., EUR),
; passing the amount and currency as separate arguments causes the currency
; symbol to be treated as an account name rather than part of the amount.
; The balancing account from past transactions (Assets:Cash) should be used,
; but instead the currency name (EUR) appears as the balancing posting.

commodity EUR
    format 1.000,00 EUR

2024/01/01 Shop
    Expenses:Food    1.500,00 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test xact 2024/02/01 Shop 1000 EUR
2024/02/01 Shop
    Expenses:Food                       1.000,00 EUR
    EUR
end test
